  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The weight of sample A is <math alttext=\"468 percent sign\"><mn>468</mn><mo>%</mo></math> of the weight of sample B, and the weight of sample A is <math alttext=\"0.780 percent sign\"><mn>0.780</mn><mo>%</mo></math> of the weight of sample C. If the weight of sample C is <math alttext=\"p percent sign\"><mi>p</mi><mo>%</mo></math> of the weight of sample B, what is the value of <math alttext=\"p\"><mi>p</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
